Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: In Aurora, multiple apartment complexes have been taken over by the savage Venezuelan prison gang known as “Tren de Aragua”—or as law enforcement calls them, “T.D.A.” Last month, six men armed with rifles and handguns were caught on camera as they forced their way into an apartment building and threatened the tenant at gunpoint. 10 minutes later, they opened fire on a 25-year-old man outside the building, fatally shooting him. Of the barbaric thugs who have been identified, at least THREE are illegal aliens who were in Border Patrol custody but were ordered RELEASED into the United States by Kamala Harris
